<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>AXIO VULN LAB - 웹 취약점 모의훈련 센터</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .hub-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }
    .hub-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .hub-title h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; }
    .hub-title h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hub-subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--text2);
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .hub-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .hub-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 36px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      transition: all .2s;
      display: block;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hub-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,200,150,.12);
    }
    .hub-card.shop:hover {
      border-color: #a78bfa;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(167,139,250,.12);
    }
    .hub-card-icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hub-card-title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .hub-card.exchange .hub-card-title { color: var(--accent); }
    .hub-card.shop .hub-card-title { color: #a78bfa; }
    .hub-card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hub-card-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
    .hub-card-tags .tag {
      padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text2);
    }
    .hub-badge {
      position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 16px;
      background: var(--accent); color: #000;
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 20px;
    }
    .hub-badge.new { background: #a78bfa; color: #fff; }
    .hub-footer {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hub-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hub-footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<div class="hub-container">
  <div class="hub-title">
    <h1>AXIO <span>VULN LAB</span></h1>
  </div>
  <p class="hub-subtitle">
    웹 취약점 진단 모의훈련 센터 · OWASP Top 10 실습 환경<br>
    훈련할 시스템을 선택하세요.
  </p>

  <div class="hub-cards">
    <a href="/dashboard" class="hub-card exchange">
      <span class="hub-badge">거래소</span>
      <div class="hub-card-icon">📈</div>
      <div class="hub-card-title">가상 암호화폐 거래소</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">
        AXIO Exchange — BTC/ETH/XRP 실시간 거래, 지갑 관리, 송금 기능을 통해
        거래소 환경의 OWASP Top 10 취약점을 실습합니다.
      </div>
      <div class="hub-card-tags">
        <span class="tag">SQLi</span>
        <span class="tag">XSS</span>
        <span class="tag">IDOR</span>
        <span class="tag">SSRF</span>
        <span class="tag">JWT</span>
        <span class="tag">CSRF</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/shop" class="hub-card shop">
      <span class="hub-badge new">쇼핑몰</span>
      <div class="hub-card-icon">🛒</div>
      <div class="hub-card-title">가상 쇼핑몰</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">
        AXIO Mall — 상품 검색, 장바구니, 결제, 리뷰 시스템을 통해
        이커머스 환경의 OWASP Top 10 취약점을 실습합니다.
      </div>
      <div class="hub-card-tags">
        <span class="tag">SQLi 검색</span>
        <span class="tag">XSS 리뷰</span>
        <span class="tag">IDOR 주문</span>
        <span class="tag">가격조작</span>
        <span class="tag">CSRF</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="hub-footer">
    <div class="card" style="text-align:center">
      <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">10</div>
      <div style="color:var(--text2);font-size:13px">OWASP 카테고리</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="text-align:center">
      <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">20+</div>
      <div style="color:var(--text2);font-size:13px">취약점 시나리오</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="text-align:center">
      <a href="/challenges" style="text-decoration:none">
        <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">🚩</div>
        <div style="color:var(--text2);font-size:13px">챌린지 도전</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:24px">
    <div class="card-title">기본 계정 정보 (훈련용)</div>
    <table>
      <tr><th>아이디</th><th>비밀번호</th><th>권한</th></tr>
      <tr><td>admin</td><td>admin1234</td><td><span class="badge admin">admin</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td>alice</td><td>(MD5 해시)</td><td><span class="badge">user</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td>testuser</td><td>test1234</td><td><span class="badge">user</span></td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
